TEXT.S: nalecuh i Oakland, California ciniza. nanusyubay kanas-malimiunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Drew Barry i 1996 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka tusa ku uwac atu silsil lima a bataan izaw ku pitu(57), namapili' tu nu Seattle SuperSonics putiput. 2 bulad 17 demiad, 1973 a mihca, Drew Barry, miunduay.
